---
layout: base.njk
permalink: "contact.html"
title: "Contact Us | Tampa Bay Property Experts"
description: "Contact Tampa Bay Property Experts. Call 813.390.0893 or send a message about property management, leasing, or maintenance in the greater Tampa Bay area."
---
<section class="phero" style="padding:58px 0 50px"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a> › Contact</div>
  <h1>Get in touch</h1>
  <p>Questions about managing your property, renting a home, or a current lease? We're here to help.</p>
</div></section>

<section><div class="wrap" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:.9fr 1.1fr;gap:46px;align-items:start">
  <div>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.7rem;margin-bottom:1rem">Reach us directly</h2>
    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:14px"><h3 style="font-size:1.05rem">📞 Phone</h3><p><a href="tel:{{ site.phoneRaw }}" style="color:var(--teal-d);font-weight:600">{{ site.phone }}</a><br><span style="font-size:.86rem;color:var(--muted)">{{ site.hours }}</span></p></div>
    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:14px"><h3 style="font-size:1.05rem">✉️ Email</h3><p><a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" style="color:var(--teal-d);font-weight:600">{{ site.email }}</a></p></div>
    <div class="card"><h3 style="font-size:1.05rem">📍 Office</h3><p>{{ site.addressLine }}<br><span style="font-size:.86rem;color:var(--muted)">{{ site.broker }} · License #{{ site.license }}</span></p></div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-card">
    <h2 style="font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1.2rem">Send us a message</h2>
    <form onsubmit="this.style.display='none';document.getElementById('cok').style.display='block';return false">
      <div class="frow"><div class="field"><label>Name</label><input required></div><div class="field"><label>Phone</label><input type="tel"></div></div>
      <div class="frow one"><div class="field"><label>Email</label><input type="email" required></div></div>
      <div class="frow one"><div class="field"><label>I'm a…</label><select><option>Property owner</option><option>Current tenant</option><option>Prospective renter</option><option>Other</option></select></div></div>
      <div class="frow one"><div class="field"><label>Message</label><textarea rows="4" required></textarea></div></div>
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" type="submit" style="width:100%;justify-content:center">Send Message</button>
      <p class="center" style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--muted-2);margin-top:.7rem">Demo form — at launch this delivers straight to your inbox.</p>
    </form>
    <div id="cok" style="display:none;text-align:center;padding:24px"><div style="font-size:2.4rem">✅</div><h3>Message sent!</h3><p style="color:var(--muted)">We'll get back to you shortly.</p></div>
  </div>
</div></section>
